<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Photo → Gradient Background</title>
<style>
  :root{--bg:#0e0e10;--panel:#17171b;--line:#2a2a31;--fg:#eaeaea;--mut:#9a9aa3;--acc:#c9b8ff;}
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html,body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--fg);font:14px/1.5 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Pretendard","Noto Sans KR",sans-serif}
  .wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;display:grid;gap:20px;grid-template-columns:1fr}
  @media(min-width:820px){.wrap{grid-template-columns:420px 1fr}}
  h1{font-size:16px;margin:0 0 4px;letter-spacing:.2px}
  p.sub{color:var(--mut);margin:0 0 16px;font-size:12px}
  .panel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:16px}
  label{display:block;font-size:12px;color:var(--mut);margin:14px 0 6px}
  input[type=file]{width:100%;color:var(--fg)}
  .row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .seg{display:flex;background:#111;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;width:100%}
  .seg button{flex:1;background:transparent;color:var(--fg);border:0;padding:8px 4px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap}
  .seg button.on{background:var(--acc);color:#111;font-weight:600}
  input[type=range]{width:100%}
  .palette{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .sw{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px}
  .sw b{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--line);display:block}
  .sw span{font-size:10px;color:var(--mut);font-family:ui-monospace,monospace}
  .stage{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-start}
  .frame{position:relative;width:min(100%,360px);aspect-ratio:9/16;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#000}
  .frame canvas.bg{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
  .frame img.photo{position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);max-width:78%;max-height:72%;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35)}
  .actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
  button.btn{background:var(--acc);color:#111;border:0;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}
  button.ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--fg);border:1px solid var(--line)}
  .val{color:var(--fg);float:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  .modal{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:100;padding:20px}
  .modal.on{display:flex}
  .modal-inner{background:var(--panel);border-radius:14px;padding:16px;max-width:420px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;overflow:auto}
  .modal-inner h2{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 8px}
  .modal-inner p{font-size:12px;color:var(--mut);margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.5}
  .modal-inner img{width:100%;border-radius:10px;display:block;margin-bottom:12px}
  .modal-inner .close{width:100%}
  .hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--mut);margin-top:6px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="modal" id="saveModal">
  <div class="modal-inner">
    <h2>이미지 저장</h2>
    <p>아래 이미지를 <b>길게 눌러</b> "사진에 추가"를 선택하기 바람. (iOS) · PC는 우클릭 → "이미지 저장".</p>
    <img id="saveImg" alt="gradient background"/>
    <button class="btn close" id="closeModal">닫기</button>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="wrap">
  <section class="panel">
    <h1>Photo → Gradient Background</h1>
    <p class="sub">사진의 지배색을 추출해 9:16 배경을 생성함. 사진은 색 스포이드로만 사용됨.</p>

    <label>이미지 업로드</label>
    <input id="file" type="file" accept="image/*"/>
    <div class="actions" style="margin-top:10px">
      <button class="btn" id="apply" disabled>미리보기 적용</button>
      <button class="btn ghost" id="clear">초기화</button>
    </div>
    <div class="hint" id="fileStatus">파일을 선택한 뒤 "미리보기 적용"을 눌러야 반영됨.</div>

    <label>그라데이션 방식</label>
    <div class="seg" id="modeSeg">
      <button data-v="linear" class="on">선형</button>
      <button data-v="radial">방사형</button>
      <button data-v="mesh">메쉬</button>
      <button data-v="conic">코닉</button>
      <button data-v="watercolor">수채화</button>
    </div>

    <label>채도 <span class="val" id="satV">100%</span></label>
    <input id="sat" type="range" min="40" max="300" value="100"/>

    <label>번짐(블러) <span class="val" id="blurV">60px</span></label>
    <input id="blur" type="range" min="0" max="160" value="60"/>

    <label>거침(종이 질감·안료 농도) <span class="val" id="roughV">50%</span></label>
    <input id="rough" type="range" min="0" max="200" value="50"/>

    <label>색 개수 <span class="val" id="kV">4</span></label>
    <input id="k" type="range" min="2" max="6" value="4"/>

    <label>각도 (선형/코닉) <span class="val" id="angV">135​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​
